{"published time": "2024-03-16T02:01:47+08:00", "images": ["https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plenaria.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0286-1024x683.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faixa-e-bandeira-na-frente-do-evento-1024x680.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0284-683x1024.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plateia-do-evento-2-1-1024x702.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Fala-do-juiz-aposentado-Jorge-Moreno-relator-do-Tribunal-Popular-1024x680.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0494-1-683x1024.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Tribunal-testemunha-in-loco-as-destruicoes-promovidas-pelos-grileiros-1024x680.jpg", "https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0692-1024x683.jpg"], "content": "<div class=\"el-single-thumbnail\">\n <img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1688px) 100vw, 1688px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plenaria.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plenaria.jpg 1688w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plenaria-300x199.jpg 300w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plenaria-1024x680.jpg 1024w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plenaria-768x510.jpg 768w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plenaria-1536x1020.jpg 1536w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plenaria-60x40.jpg 60w\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1121\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plenaria.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plenaria.jpg\" width=\"1688\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n <p>\n  El 9 y 10 de marzo, la victoriosa corte popular contra el agarre y los cr\u00edmenes del propietario se llevaron a cabo en la aldea de Vilela en Junco do Maranh\u00e3o. Al evento asistieron abogados populares, investigadores, sindicalistas y periodistas de otras regiones del pa\u00eds que participaron en el comit\u00e9 de jueces del tribunal.\n </p>\n <p>\n  El Tribunal tambi\u00e9n tuvo la participaci\u00f3n de diferentes organizaciones, como la Uni\u00f3n de Comunidades en Fight y los Filhos colectivos de Student Do Povo, quien organiz\u00f3 a los estudiantes para asistir al evento. El liderazgo campesino\n  <a href=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/ma-luiz-vila-nova-memorias-da-vida-e-da-luta-de-um-militante-foi-relancado-em-evento-na-ufma/\">\n   Luiz Vila Nova\n  </a>\n  Tambi\u00e9n asisti\u00f3 al evento.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171093\" data-id=\"171093\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0286-1024x683.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0286-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0286-300x200.jpg 300w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0286-768x512.jpg 768w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0286-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0286-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0286-60x40.jpg 60w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0286-720x480.jpg 720w\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0286-1024x683.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0286-1024x683.jpg\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Los campesinos extienden la pista en el evento. Foto: base de datos y\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171096\" data-id=\"171096\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faixa-e-bandeira-na-frente-do-evento-1024x680.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faixa-e-bandeira-na-frente-do-evento-1024x680.jpg 1024w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faixa-e-bandeira-na-frente-do-evento-300x199.jpg 300w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faixa-e-bandeira-na-frente-do-evento-768x510.jpg 768w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faixa-e-bandeira-na-frente-do-evento-1536x1020.jpg 1536w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faixa-e-bandeira-na-frente-do-evento-60x40.jpg 60w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faixa-e-bandeira-na-frente-do-evento.jpg 1688w\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"680\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faixa-e-bandeira-na-frente-do-evento-1024x680.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faixa-e-bandeira-na-frente-do-evento-1024x680.jpg\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    La pista de entrada del evento anunci\u00f3 el tono. Foto: base de datos y\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171089\" data-id=\"171089\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0284-683x1024.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0284-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0284-200x300.jpg 200w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0284-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0284-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0284-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0284-60x90.jpg 60w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0284-scaled.jpg 1707w\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0284-683x1024.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0284-683x1024.jpg\" width=\"683\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Los estudiantes llevaron a Caravan al evento. Foto: Foto: Base de datos y\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171094\" data-id=\"171094\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plateia-do-evento-2-1-1024x702.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plateia-do-evento-2-1-1024x702.jpg 1024w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plateia-do-evento-2-1-300x206.jpg 300w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plateia-do-evento-2-1-768x527.jpg 768w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plateia-do-evento-2-1-1536x1054.jpg 1536w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plateia-do-evento-2-1-60x41.jpg 60w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plateia-do-evento-2-1.jpg 1688w\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"702\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plateia-do-evento-2-1-1024x702.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Plateia-do-evento-2-1-1024x702.jpg\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    La bandera palestina se extendi\u00f3 al lado del carril central del evento. Foto: base de datos y\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  A lo largo del auditorio, las organizaciones banderas y pistas con consigna de la lucha de la tierra decoraron el medio ambiente. Justo en el camino de acceso, una pista\n  <strong>\n   \u00a1Fuera de las tierras de nuestras tierras! \u00a1Por el t\u00edtulo de nuestras posesiones!\n  </strong>\n  Establezca el tono del evento. Dentro del auditorio, otros rangos condenaron el agarre, la gran miner\u00eda y pidieron la uni\u00f3n de los campesinos. Las firmas eran de ocupantes ilegales de diferentes comunidades, como Gleba Campina, Vilela Village, Caranandeua y Jaraquara Communities y la asociaci\u00f3n de agricultores de la aldea de Maracacura, el municipio de Carutapera.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171095\" data-id=\"171095\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Fala-do-juiz-aposentado-Jorge-Moreno-relator-do-Tribunal-Popular-1024x680.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Fala-do-juiz-aposentado-Jorge-Moreno-relator-do-Tribunal-Popular-1024x680.jpg 1024w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Fala-do-juiz-aposentado-Jorge-Moreno-relator-do-Tribunal-Popular-300x199.jpg 300w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Fala-do-juiz-aposentado-Jorge-Moreno-relator-do-Tribunal-Popular-768x510.jpg 768w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Fala-do-juiz-aposentado-Jorge-Moreno-relator-do-Tribunal-Popular-1536x1020.jpg 1536w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Fala-do-juiz-aposentado-Jorge-Moreno-relator-do-Tribunal-Popular-60x40.jpg 60w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Fala-do-juiz-aposentado-Jorge-Moreno-relator-do-Tribunal-Popular.jpg 1688w\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"680\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Fala-do-juiz-aposentado-Jorge-Moreno-relator-do-Tribunal-Popular-1024x680.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Fala-do-juiz-aposentado-Jorge-Moreno-relator-do-Tribunal-Popular-1024x680.jpg\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Hablando del juez jubilado Jorge Moreno, relator de la corte popular. Foto: base de datos y\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171097\" data-id=\"171097\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0494-1-683x1024.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0494-1-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0494-1-200x300.jpg 200w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0494-1-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0494-1-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0494-1-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0494-1-60x90.jpg 60w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0494-1-scaled.jpg 1707w\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0494-1-683x1024.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0494-1-683x1024.jpg\" width=\"683\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Liderazgo campesino Luiz Vila Nova particip\u00f3 en la corte popular. Foto: base de datos y\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  En una de las actividades del evento, los campesinos organizaron una caravana de motocicleta para visitar la Campina de Gleba y determinar los cr\u00edmenes promovidos por los acaparadores de tierras.\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171099\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Tribunal-testemunha-in-loco-as-destruicoes-promovidas-pelos-grileiros-1024x680.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Tribunal-testemunha-in-loco-as-destruicoes-promovidas-pelos-grileiros-1024x680.jpg 1024w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Tribunal-testemunha-in-loco-as-destruicoes-promovidas-pelos-grileiros-300x199.jpg 300w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Tribunal-testemunha-in-loco-as-destruicoes-promovidas-pelos-grileiros-768x510.jpg 768w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Tribunal-testemunha-in-loco-as-destruicoes-promovidas-pelos-grileiros-1536x1020.jpg 1536w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Tribunal-testemunha-in-loco-as-destruicoes-promovidas-pelos-grileiros-60x40.jpg 60w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Tribunal-testemunha-in-loco-as-destruicoes-promovidas-pelos-grileiros.jpg 1688w\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"680\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Tribunal-testemunha-in-loco-as-destruicoes-promovidas-pelos-grileiros-1024x680.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Tribunal-testemunha-in-loco-as-destruicoes-promovidas-pelos-grileiros-1024x680.jpg\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Los testigos de la corte en el lugar la destrucci\u00f3n promovida por los acaparadores de tierras. Foto: base de datos y\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n  Como derivaci\u00f3n de la corte popular, las organizaciones actuales llamaron un d\u00eda de movilizaci\u00f3n y luchan contra la ley de grado estatal de Maranh\u00e3o al 1 de mayo. La nota se puede leer\n  <a href=\"https://medium.com/@comsolute/nota-conjunta-abaixo-a-lei-da-grilagem-35783ca1efa7\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">\n   en su totalidad aqu\u00ed\n  </a>\n  .\n </p>\n <p>\n  del pueblo; al producir asistente material legal a la causa de las comunidades; al sacudir los presentes alrededor de la solidaridad con la lucha por la tierra \".\n </p>\n <p>\n  La nota tambi\u00e9n hace un c\u00e1lido saludo al colectivo de estudiante Filhos do Povo, quien tom\u00f3 un autob\u00fas lleno de estudiantes. Seg\u00fan el presente, el tribunal popular fue un hito en el desarrollo del nuevo movimiento estudiantil en Maranh\u00e3o.\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-171092\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" data-lazy-src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0692-1024x683.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0692-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0692-300x200.jpg 300w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0692-768x512.jpg 768w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0692-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0692-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0692-60x40.jpg 60w, https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0692-720x480.jpg 720w\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0692-1024x683.jpg\" srcset=\"https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/IMG_0692-1024x683.jpg\" width=\"1024\"/>\n   <figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">\n    Los participantes celebran durante la actividad cultural. Foto: base de datos y\n   </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n</div>\n", "source": "https://anovademocracia.com.br/tribunal-popular-junco-maranhao/", "type": "article", "title": "El tribunal popular contra los cr\u00edmenes de grado y latifundio en Junco do Maranh\u00e3o - La nueva democracia", "description": "Al evento asistieron abogados populares, investigadores, sindicalistas y periodistas de otras regiones del pa\u00eds que participaron en el comit\u00e9 de jueces del tribunal.", "modified time": "2024-03-15T15:22:11-03:00", "updated time": "2024-03-15T15:22:11-03:00", "author": ["Comit\u00ea de Apoio \u2013 S\u00e3o Lu\u00eds (MA)"], "categories": ["Luta Pela Terra"], "tags": ["grilagem", "Pistolagem"], "sections": ["Luta Pela Terra"], "link-section": "luta-pela-terra", "source_name": "A Nova Democracia"}